title: Beinn Tulaichean
text: Beinn Tulaichean is a <a href="Scotland">Scottish</a> <a href="mountain">mountain</a>. It is not much more than the southern top of <a href="Cruach%20Ardrain">Cruach Ardrain</a>, with a descent of only 120m before the ascent to its larger neighbour. It is located approximately 10 km to the north of <a href="Loch%20Katrine">Loch Katrine</a> close to the site of <a href="Robert%20Roy%20MacGregor">Robert Roy MacGregor</a>'s house.
